<DIV>If you are a Legend's Subscriber, please vote in the poll when you log into EverQuest.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The poll will state something similar to this:</DIV>
<DIV><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#cccccc></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#cccccc>As of January 31st, 2006 we will be discontinuing the Legends service.&nbsp; We know that the Stormhammer server means a lot to the people playing on it, so we wanted to get your input into the future of the server after the service has been discontinued.&nbsp; Please vote for one of the two options below.</FONT></SPAN></DIV>
<DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#cccccc>&nbsp;· Close down the Stormhammer server when the Legends service is discontinued and allow us to transfer to the server of our choice. </FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#cccccc>&nbsp;· Keep Stormhammer available as a server when the Legends service is discontinued and begin allowing new transfers to our server. </FONT></SPAN></P></DIV>
				
							<p>Kytherea ~~wielding a giant hammer & a hairless War Hamster~~<br><br>"I'm late, I'm late...."
							
